                               <div class="panel-heading clearfix"><h4 class="panel-title" style="text-align: center"><strong>Stephen Buchanan</strong></div><img src="vnfruini" class="img-responsive"/><div class="list-group">
                               <div class="list-group-item">
                               <h4 class="list-group-item-heading">Treasurer</h4><h4 class="list-group-item-heading">Sophomore</h4></div><div class="list-group-item">
                               <p class="list-group-item-text">Stephen Buchanan is a sophomore at Duxbury High school, and he is the treasurer and is part of the fabrication team on the Duxbury robotics team. He is in his first year on the robotics team.  Stephen is a fan of playing video games. Stephen is a part of the Concert band in the Duxbury High School, where he plays the saxophone. Stephen is also a boy scout in the Duxbury boy scout troop.</p>
                               </div>
                               </div>
                               </div>
                               </div><!-- ID:41} Type: 1--><div class="col-lg-4">
