                               <div class="list-group-item">
                               <h4 class="list-group-item-heading">Parts/Shop Manager; Director of Purchasing</h4><h4 class="list-group-item-heading">Freshman</h4></div><div class="list-group-item">
                               <p class="list-group-item-text">Mike is new here and is ready to start in the robotics team. His marks and buys things for the team, as well as organizing pieces and parts. Outside of robotics, he is not currently playing a sport, but has played every sport the school offers at one point or another. He has made honor roll every year and is a very organized person. Mike is new to the team and hopes to find ways to help.</p>
                               </div>
                               </div>
                               </div>
