                               <div class="list-group-item">
                               <h4 class="list-group-item-heading">Webmaster, Integration Coordinator</h4><h4 class="list-group-item-heading">Freshman</h4></div><div class="list-group-item">
                               <p class="list-group-item-text">Henry is entering his first year with the team as a freshman after participating as a middle school robotics club captain last season. Henry has participated in Duxbury Middle School’s FIRST Lego competitions and in took part in their weekly meetings. He also took classes in the middle school STEM program and is taking programming and engineering electives during the 2015-2016 school year. Henry played soccer for the freshman team this fall, and hopes to continue playing the sport in the spring and throughout his high school career.</p>
