                               <p class="list-group-item-text">Dylan is a freshman new to the Duxbury School system. He loves pancakes, and his favorite subjects in school include Woodshop, TV Studio, History, and Science. When not at school he enjoys fishing, skiing, and hiking. Oil painting is an uncommon hobby of his which he has been perfecting since he was 7. He aspires to someday have a career in aquaculture, because it is becoming a huge industry with many obstacles.</p>
